author: @sanukiweerakkody7634
text: Dear Blackpink, this message that i am writing to you is not fake, so pls hear me out. Ever since you first released your first song, I fell in love with you all. You all were the first people to ever get me interested in K-pop. I have been a blink for so long that I couldn't even count the years I was a blink. I have a big passion for piano, and I have tried all of your songs by ear, but I was forbidden from my parents to upload it. And just so you know i live in the UAE and I study in UAE, i am originally form Sri Lanka, when I heard that BLACKPINK was finally doing a world tour, I got so excited that I went many webpages to check if you were coming to the UAE, and there you have it you were coming to Abu Dhabi the capital of the UAE, at Etihad (I think) the stage area. It was on the 28th of January. When I heard this, I got super excited that looking at the message, I almost fell off my chair. I have a big passion for art too so I think you can guessthe next step,  I painted all members in one painting and then all members in separate paintings and I thought to myself that when I come in that day, if I had the opportunity, I would love to give it you all but sadly I had my school concert on the same day. Tbh, I cried so much that day because I missed a lifetime opportunity. A month before my birthday, my father went to South Korea and went to Soeul just to get me Blackpink merchandise, and on the special day, I received these wonderful gifts. Now, a lot of you may think that I am an obsessed fan. Well, don't think in that way, I just really love them, their music well, basically everything. In conclusion to my dear Blackpink, I wish you a safe, fun, enjoyable, and healthy life ahead. Be free to do what you love cause that is what you live for. Say bye-bye to haters and hello blinks. As a Blink, I will cherish you in my heart forever. You will never be forgotten, not just by me, even others will cherish you and keep you all in our hearts forever. We are here to support you no matter what odds go by. Stay safe and have a lovely day. WE LOVE Y'ALL SO MUCH
